{"tid":708433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"核突阿叔好痕　巴士除鞋用扶手腳底按摩","createTime":"2018-06-19T10:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:40:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81643b9b8381992e66f61d5de1fb4cf078b66060","tid":708433,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619154042854-0619_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180619175524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619154042854-0619_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180619175524&h=9c01acfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下層巴士乘客雙腳「飛象過河」將雙腳放在對面座位上外，又有巴士阿返再創絕技。有乘客今早（19日）發現，一個巴士阿叔竟除鞋將腳板底踹在對面座椅的扶手打圈，令他可以一邊坐巴士、一邊自製免費腳底按摩的升級享受。縱使旁邊有乘客也毫不在意，如人無人之境。 <br />\n<br />\n上傳的網友指影片由其公司同事，於今晨6時許乘搭沙田去觀塘的89號線雙層九巴上拍攝，當時該中年男子一直將脫掉鞋子、只穿着灰色襪子的右腳踹在對面座椅的扶手上，直言阿叔除鞋按摩好臭，更懷疑對方有香港腳，以後不敢再亂用扶手。 <br />\n<br />\n「佢捽腳底捽得好忘我！」不少網民評論其在巴士腳底按摩的的行為，不少人直呼阿叔行為令人作嘔及自私。有人則直指阿叔腳板底一直踹的穴位，是用以改善腎虧，東網翻查腳底按摩穴位圖時確認，是改善腎臟經絡的位置。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180619/bkn-20180619154042854-0619_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180619%2Fbkn-20180619154042854-0619_00822_001.html&d=IYB1KEC4QVtgI8ppafVNdgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=51dc5d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180619/bkn-20180619154042854-0619_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"70bddd7125e66015a5ef5cb4a631af0848e12d29","tid":708433,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"阿叔個腎唔得有冇錢買偉哥 <br />\n<br />\n唔襯機會督下佢 一陣點去叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6eb8ff208d5945cdebd2c3e270279006b3d2b64","tid":708433,"uid":52943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">東網翻查腳底按摩穴位圖時確認，是改善腎臟經絡的位置。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9671b263ec2961ab40993214aafcf16048c2feb8","tid":708433,"uid":174115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"屌，用愛膚堅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece08ebc09322660f0d26c0182145593dc4c1b50","tid":708433,"uid":53958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9671b263ec2961ab40993214aafcf16048c2feb8","tid":708433,"uid":174115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"屌，用愛膚堅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用黑旋風"},{"pid":"40e3bac6897773cdab3332895581fcbfa94838f4","tid":708433,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6eb8ff208d5945cdebd2c3e270279006b3d2b64","tid":708433,"uid":52943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">東網翻查腳底按摩穴位圖時確認，是改善腎臟經絡的位置。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"on.99"},{"pid":"ba8edd78dfdf5542a7b96437c9e9b89e5f44b8dc","tid":708433,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"東網係咪想同嗰位啊叔鬥戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4386788f81b02075c7e61a772a8cf96f265cc28e","tid":708433,"uid":55090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:40:20.000